---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Support - Empire Inc"
  description="Get help with Empire Inc. Contact our support team for questions, bug reports, and feedback."
>
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-slate-950 text-white py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Support</h1>

      <p class="text-slate-400 mb-8">
        Need help with Empire Inc? Find answers to common questions below or contact us directly.
      </p>

      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">1. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>For any questions, issues, or feedback:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Email: <a href="mailto:support@empireinc.app" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">support@empireinc.app</a></li>
          </ul>
          <p>We typically respond within 24 hours.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">2. Subscriptions</h2>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">2.1 How to Restore Purchases</h3>
          <p>
            Go to the Premium screen in the app and tap "Restore Purchases" at the bottom. Make sure you are signed in with the same Apple ID or Google account used for the original purchase.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 mt-4">2.2 How to Cancel a Subscription</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>iOS:</strong> Settings &gt; Apple ID &gt; Subscriptions &gt; Empire Inc &gt; Cancel Subscription</li>
            <li><strong>Android:</strong> Google Play Store &gt; Menu &gt; Subscriptions &gt; Empire Inc &gt; Cancel</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            Cancellation takes effect at the end of the current billing period. You will continue to have access until then.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 mt-4">2.3 Refunds</h3>
          <p>
            All purchases are processed through the Apple App Store or Google Play Store. For refund requests, please contact Apple or Google directly through their respective support channels.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">3. Account</h2>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">3.1 Delete Your Account</h3>
          <p>
            Go to Settings in the app and scroll down to "Delete Account". This will permanently delete your account and all associated data. This action cannot be undone.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 mt-4">3.2 Progress Not Saving</h3>
          <p>
            Make sure you have a stable internet connection. Your game progress is saved to our servers automatically. If the issue persists, try closing and reopening the app or contact us at <a href="mailto:support@empireinc.app" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">support@empireinc.app</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">4. Reporting Issues</h2>
          <p>
            If you encounter a bug or crash, please email us at <a href="mailto:support@empireinc.app" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">support@empireinc.app</a> with the following information:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Description of the issue</li>
            <li>Your device model and OS version</li>
            <li>Steps to reproduce the problem</li>
            <li>Screenshots or screen recordings (if possible)</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">5. Legal</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li><a href="/privacy" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><a href="/terms" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">Terms of Service</a></li>
          </ul>
        </section>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-slate-800">
        <p class="text-slate-400">Empire Inc</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
